I had the opportunity to download the Nyon Icon pack this week! And I have to say that I am blown away by the each Icon pack presented for each APP on my new Samsung Galaxy Note 20 Ultra! This is by far the best Icon pack I have ever seen!! There were a few APPS that did not have a set icon available to match the description. But that is something I can live with! But all remaining APPS had an amazing ICON! The ICON pack makes my phone look amazing!! Can't wait to see more future icons!

This app has prompted me to give my first written review in 7 years. Usually, I change my icons every 6 months - I can't seem to bring myself with this one; I've had this one for well over a year now. Awesome work, dev!!!
